{
  "name": "Alexa — Announce (ClinicAI)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "alexa-announce",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "responseData": "allEntries",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook: Alexa Announce",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 300],
      "webhookId": "alexa-announce"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $env.ALEXA_API_URL || 'http://localhost:3456' }}/api/announce",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            },
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "Bearer {{ $env.ALEXA_API_TOKEN || '' }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"device\": \"{{ $json.body.device || $json.body.reception_device || '' }}\",\n  \"message\": \"{{ $json.body.message || $json.body.welcome_message || '' }}\",\n  \"type\": \"{{ $json.body.type || 'announce' }}\"\n}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000,
          "allowUnauthorizedCerts": false
        }
      },
      "id": "forward-to-bridge",
      "name": "Forward to Alexa Bridge",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [500, 300],
      "continueOnFail": true
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook: Alexa Announce": {
      "main": [
        [{ "node": "Forward to Alexa Bridge", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "staticData": null,
  "tags": [
    { "name": "alexa" },
    { "name": "automation" }
  ],
  "_comment": [
    "Workflow simplificado: recebe POST com {device, message, type}",
    "e encaminha diretamente para o Alexa Bridge.",
    "",
    "A engine do dashboard ja resolve o device alvo e renderiza a mensagem.",
    "Cada request = 1 device = 1 announce.",
    "",
    "VARIAVEIS DE AMBIENTE:",
    "  ALEXA_API_URL   = http://alexa-bridge:3456 (ou IP local)",
    "  ALEXA_API_TOKEN = clinicai-alexa-2026",
    "",
    "Tambem aceita formato legado (patient_arrived) para compatibilidade."
  ]
}
